==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hitherto
<hw>Hith"er*to`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To
this place; to a prescribed limit.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Hitherto</qex> shalt thou come, but no further.</q>
<rj><qau>Job xxxviii. 11.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Up to this time; as yet; until now.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The Lord hath blessed me <qex>hitherto</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Josh.
xvii. 14.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hitherward</ent>⟦br⟧
